OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783700375
OL,3,CScheme to encourage more people to
OL,4,Cwork in NHS showing success in Cumbria
OL,6,FThe NHS says a scheme encouraging more
OL,7,Fyoung people to pursue medical careers
OL,8,Fin Cumbria is proving successful.
OL,10,FAround 70 teenagers aged between 16
OL,11,Fand 18 attended an event at Carlisle's
OL,12,FCumberland Infirmary in Carlisle to
OL,13,Ffind out about the different paths
OL,14,Favailable.
OL,16,FThe NHS is hoping that these types of
OL,17,Fevents will encourage them to stay and
OL,18,Fwork in the county.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
