OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783700375
OL,3,CScheme to encourage more people to
OL,4,Cwork in NHS showing success in Cumbria
OL,6,FThe students were given talks from a
OL,7,Frange of services including
OL,8,Forthopaedics, cardiology, maternity,
OL,9,Fsurgery and GP's.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Dr Louise
OL,12,FBuchanan said: "The career in medicine
OL,13,Fevent here at the Cumberland Infirmary
OL,14,Fis for students in year 11 and 12 who
OL,15,Fare considering medicine as a career.
OL,26,@tD@POU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783700375
OL,3,CScheme to encourage more people to
OL,4,Cwork in NHS showing success in Cumbria
OL,6,F"This allows them to meet clinicians
OL,7,Fat different career stages and also to
OL,8,Fhave some practical sessions. The
OL,9,Fpractical sessions will see them
OL,10,Fdeliver babies, fixing bones and
OL,11,Fpracticing their suturing skills this
OL,12,Fafternoon.
OL,14,F"We have had some positive feedback
OL,15,Fbut really we have had some of our
OL,16,Fjunior doctors come through our
OL,17,Fprogramme and are working in Cumbria."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
