PN,32804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783700375
OL,3,CScheme to encourage more people to
OL,4,Cwork in NHS showing success in Cumbria
OL,6,FDr Jenny Little attended one of the
OL,7,Fworkshops almost 10 years ago as an
OL,8,Faspiring student. She is now working
OL,9,Fback in Carlisle in the NHS and is a
OL,10,Fpositive example of success from the
OL,11,Fscheme.
OL,13,FShe said: "I actually attended this
OL,14,Fevent in 2017 when I was in sixth form
OL,15,Fand today I delivered a talk to the
OL,16,Fstudents which was a bit of a full
OL,17,Fcircle moment.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
