CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1783700375
OL,3,CScheme to encourage more people to
OL,4,Cwork in NHS showing success in Cumbria
OL,6,F"I went to medical school down in
OL,7,FNorwich for five years and did my
OL,8,Ffoundation training there and moved
OL,9,Fback up here in August and now work in
OL,10,FCarlisle."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
